Files: include/ffnvcodec/dynlink_cuda.h
       include/ffnvcodec/dynlink_loader.h
Copyright: 2016, Timo Rothenpieler
License: Expat
Comment:
 This files orignate from ffmpeg and implement the loader. They were introduced in ffmpeg in commit
 5c02d2827bef81ba3f3582d67ec7693067985f9e and authored by Timo Rothenpieler. They have been split
 off from ffmpeg as nv-codec-headers together with the NVENC/NVDEC API definitions.

